<Layout title="Refund Policy - Psychology Zone">
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="header">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/" class="logo">
          <span class="logo-text">Psychology<span class="highlight">Zone</span></span>
        </a>
        <div class="nav-spacer"></div>
        <a href="tel:+918968900002" class="phone-link">
          <span class="phone-icon">ðŸ“ž</span>
          <span class="phone-number">+91 89689 00002</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book My Session</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Refund Policy</h1>
        <p>We are committed to your satisfaction. Please review our refund policy below.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content -->
    <section class="page-content">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-box">
          <h2>1. Refund Eligibility</h2>
          <p>Psychology Zone offers refunds under the following conditions:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Refunds are available for cancelled sessions up to 24 hours before the scheduled appointment time</li>
            <li>If a therapist cancels a session without valid reason, you will receive a full refund or credit for a rescheduled session</li>
            <li>Technical issues preventing the session from occurring qualify for a full refund or rescheduling</li>
            <li>Payment disputes must be raised within 7 days of the transaction</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>2. Refund Process</h2>
          <p>To request a refund, please follow these steps:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@psychologyzone.in">info@psychologyzone.in</a> or <a href="tel:+918968900002">+91 89689 00002</a></li>
            <li>Provide your session details, booking reference, and reason for refund request</li>
            <li>Include any supporting documentation if applicable</li>
            <li>Our team will review your request within 5-7 business days</li>
            <li>If approved, refunds will be processed to your original payment method within 10-15 business days</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>3. Non-Refundable Scenarios</h2>
          <p>The following situations are generally non-refundable:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Refunds cannot be issued if you cancel within 24 hours of a scheduled session</li>
            <li>No-shows without prior notification are non-refundable</li>
            <li>Sessions already completed are non-refundable</li>
            <li>Client-initiated cancellations with less than 24 hours notice are subject to retention of payment</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>4. Session Credits & Rescheduling</h2>
          <p>Instead of a refund, you may prefer:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Rescheduling your session to another date and time</li>
            <li>Receiving a credit towards future sessions</li>
            <li>Converting your payment into session credits with valid up to 3 months</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>5. Payment Method & Processing</h2>
          <p>Refunds will be processed to the original payment method used for the transaction. Depending on your bank or payment provider, it may take 5-10 business days for the refund to appear in your account. We are not responsible for delays caused by your financial institution.</p>

          <h2>6. Package Deals & Discounts</h2>
          <p>If you have purchased a package or used promotional codes:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Only unused portions of packages are eligible for refund</li>
            <li>Discounted packages have limited refund eligibility (contact us for details)</li>
            <li>Promotional credits are non-transferable and non-refundable</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>7. Dispute Resolution</h2>
          <p>If you believe you are entitled to a refund and your request is denied:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>You may request a formal review by emailing us with detailed documentation</li>
            <li>We will respond with a detailed explanation within 10 business days</li>
            <li>You may escalate the matter for independent review if you remain unsatisfied</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>8. Money-Back Guarantee</h2>
          <p>Psychology Zone offers a satisfaction guarantee. If you are not satisfied with your first session and provide feedback within 24 hours, we will either:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Offer you a full refund, or</li>
            <li>Match you with a different therapist at no additional cost</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>9. Cancellation by Psychology Zone</h2>
          <p>If we cancel a session:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>We will provide at least 48 hours' notice whenever possible</li>
            <li>You will receive a full refund or credit for a rescheduled session</li>
            <li>We will provide alternative time slots or refund the payment immediately</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>10. Contact Us for Refund Inquiries</h2>
          <div class="contact-info">
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@psychologyzone.in">info@psychologyzone.in</a></p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+918968900002">+91 89689 00002</a></p>
            <p><strong>Address:</strong> Arjun Singh Bajwa 20, Sector 8A, Chandigarh, India</p>
            <p><strong>Hours:</strong> Monday - Sunday, 9:00 AM - 9:00 PM IST</p>
          </div>

          <h2>11. Policy Changes</h2>
          <p>Psychology Zone reserves the right to modify this Refund Policy at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to the website. Continued use of our services following policy updates constitutes acceptance of the new terms.</p>

          <p style="margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; color: var(--text-light); font-size: 0.9rem;">Last Modified: December 2024</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-content">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <p style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 15px;">Psychology<span style="color: var(--primary-color);">Zone</span></p>
          <p>Your partner in mental well-being â€“ Providing accessible, comprehensive support for a healthier mind and life.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer-cta">
          <h4>Ready to Start Your Journey?</h4>
          <p>Take the first step towards better mental health today.</p>
          <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book My Session</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer-connect">
          <h4>Contact Us</h4>
          <p>Arjun Singh Bajwa 20 sector 8A Chandigarh</p>
          <p><a href="tel:+918968900002">+91 89689 00002</a></p>
          <p><a href="mailto:info@psychologyzone.in">info@psychologyzone.in</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; 2024 <strong>Psychology Zone CHD</strong>. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        <div class="footer-legal">
          <a href="/contact/">Contact</a>
          <a href="/terms-and-conditions/">Terms & Conditions</a>
          <a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>
          <a href="/refund-policy/">Refund Policy</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff7ed 0%, #ffedd5 100%);
    padding: 100px 0;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 80px;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  }

  .page-hero p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .page-content {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .content-box {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-box h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  }

  .content-box h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .content-box p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .content-box ul {
    list-style-position: inside;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .content-box ul li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .content-box a {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .content-box a:hover {
    color: var(--primary-dark);
  }

  .contact-info {
    background: var(--accent-cream);
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  /* Header */
  .header {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(44, 53, 57, 0.04);
    z-index: 1000;
  }

  .nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 18px 0;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .nav-spacer {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .logo-text {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  .phone-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    background: var(--accent-cream);
    border-radius: 24px;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 13px 28px;
    border-radius: 26px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(209, 122, 92, 0.25);
  }

  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    color: white;
    padding: 60px 0 30px;
  }

  .footer-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1.5fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .footer-brand p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .footer-cta {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 30px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: 15px;
  }

  .footer-cta h4 {
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .footer-cta p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .footer-connect h4 {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .footer-connect p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .footer-connect a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: 30px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .footer-bottom p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  }

  .footer-legal {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .footer-legal a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .footer-legal a:hover {
    color: white;
  }

  :root {
    --primary-color: #D17A5C;
    --primary-dark: #B85C3E;
    --secondary-color: #2C3539;
    --text-light: #6B7F8A;
    --accent-cream: #F5F1E8;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .content-box h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
